I recently discovered the best TV program ever - Orangutan Jungle School, which follows the rehabilitation/care of orphaned orangutans so they can be released safely into the wild. The school is run by @bosfoundation who are doing all they can to prevent orangutans extinction. After watching the show I've gone and adopted Valentino, one of the stars! (Through @bos_uk ) Adoption starts at ¬£3/month so now when I get the urge to buy something from the local bakery instead I'm going to resist and know that money is going somewhere more important.
Check out the show on 4OD, and consider helping support their work!
#orangutanjungleschool #saveorangutans #orangutans #criticallyendangered #animalart #animalsketch #digitalart #digitalillustration

(üîä sound on)
So last year I bought (from a well known online retailer) Substance, Peter Hook's account of his time in New Order. My friend also decided to read it at the same time, and his copy arrived before mine, so to taunt me he sent me audio messages of what he claimed were quotes from the book. They made me laugh, so I used them to make this animation... He doesn't know yet that I used his audios.

Needless to say, it's not a very accurate representation of the book, which was a hugely enjoyable read that I recommend to anyone who likes reading about musicians. Definitely no disrespect intended to the man himself @peterhook_thelight üé∏üéõÔ∏èüéπüéôÔ∏è

I was very happy to work on the animation with @sbezos for this year's EchaUnaPata campaign for @patasbox, raising money for food for abandoned dogs.
Today is the last day of the campaign (9th Dec) but you can still get involved by uploading a photo (or in this case drawing) of your pet dog, tagging @patasbox
and using the hashtag #echaunapata19
